The paper discusses machine learning models and proposes neural network-based algorithms for undersampling to tackle the class imbalance problem. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), and data structures (cs.DS).
